##### MF3: REACTION CROSS SECTIONS                                6137 1451
                                                                  6137 1451
All the data present in the following MT-sections have been       6137 1451
calculated with TALYS, possibly normalized to experimental data.  6137 1451
If the maximal cross section in an excitation function over the   6137 1451
whole energy range does not exceed 1.e-9 b, the MT-number is not  6137 1451
included. Cross sections lower than 1.e-20 b are assumed to have  6137 1451
no physical meaning and are set to zero. All MT numbers extend up 6137 1451
to the highest incident energy.                                   6137 1451
